description: Try our easy to follow Thai Fish Bruschetta recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Thai Fish Bruschetta Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place Thai salad on top of sourdough slices and top with snow peas, barramundi and tomatoes to serve. Note: The dressing provided with this product is not required for this recipe. Refrigerate it and use it for another salad within its use-by date range.
